rows.label: bf05470100_0030
rows.name: Invidian army! So many of them!

rows.label: bf05470100_0060
rows.name: Shit! Who gave that damn order?!

rows.label: bf05470100_0070
rows.name: At this rate, I don't think there's any stopping them.

rows.label: bf05470100_0090
rows.name: They think Superbia attacked them illegally.

rows.label: bf05470100_0110
rows.name:
This is bad. If someone doesn't
explain what's really going on...

rows.label: bf05470100_0120
rows.name: But there's no time for that!

rows.label: bf05470100_0130
rows.name: There has to be some way!

rows.label: bf05470100_0140
rows.name:
Heavy cannons!
That's Invidia's main weapon.

rows.label: bf05470100_0150
rows.name:
Here, too!
Superbia also readying artillery!

rows.label: bf05470100_0160
rows.name: I don't care if we're not going to make it in time!

rows.label: bf05470100_0170
rows.name: We need to get to Invidia!
